definitions.definition: A town on the Firth of Clyde , Argyll and Bute council area, Scotland ( OS grid ref NS1776 ) .
A township in the City of Cape Town , Western Cape province, South Africa .
A village in the City of Lismore , Northern Rivers region, New South Wales , Australia .
